Package: ProcessSpace
Type: Package
Title: A package to process LiDAR for stream and meadow restoration visualizations.
BugReports: https://github.com/adamkc/ProcessSpace/issues
Version: 0.1.02
Date: 2020-06-15
Author: Adam Cummings <adam.cummings@usda.gov>
Maintainer: Adam Cummings <adam.cummings@usda.gov>
Description: This package uses high resolution LiDAR terrain data and a
     stream flow network shapefile to generate detrended elevation rasters and
     polygons showing potential process space (space potentially available to
     hydrologic processes with only minor stream flow perturbations). These
     spatial data are exported as KMZ files that enable 3D interaction in
     Google Earth. 
